Package model

Class User

java.lang.Object
model.User
Direct Known Subclasses:
UserPremium, UserStandard
public abstract class User extends Object
An abstract class representing a User. It contains information about the user's ID, name, and linking date. It also maintains lists of products, cart, bills, and reading sessions associated with the user. Additionally, it holds a reference to the user's library.
